            "id": "string",
            "label": "String",
            "definition": "A string is a finite sequence of symbols drawn from an alphabet. Because it is a sequence, order matters, so two strings with the same symbols in different orders are different strings.",
            "intuition": "A string is an ordered list of symbols.",
            "importance": 0.96,
