            "definition": "The empty language, denoted by the empty set symbol, is the language containing no strings at all. It is a language with size zero, in contrast to a language that contains the empty string.",
            "intuition": "No strings belong to it.",
            "importance": 0.92,
            "depth": "deep_dive",
